item.title: Lyrics-finder
item.description: Lyrics-finder Find the lyrics for any song! Made with Reactjs and context-api Screenshots About the project The website can be used to find lyrics for any song. Type in a song title and the list of all matching songs will be listed. This was my first Reactjs project. I wanted to learn reactjs and was curious about the working of context-api. Technologies used: Reactjs, context-api, Bootstrap
